[00:00.42]	[Rome. A public place.,]
[00:01.28]	[Enter MENENIUS, COMINIUS, SICINIUS, BRUTUS,
[00:01.71]	+ and others]
[00:02.13]MENENIUS	No, I'll not go: you hear what he hath said
[00:05.56]	Which was sometime his general; who loved him
[00:09.19]	In a most dear particular. He call'd me father:
[00:12.90]	But what o' that? Go, you that banish'd him;
[00:16.25]	A mile before his tent fall down, and knee
[00:19.68]	The way into his mercy: nay, if he coy'd
[00:22.89]	To hear Cominius speak, I'll keep at home.
[00:26.24]COMINIUS	He would not seem to know me.
[00:28.73]MENENIUS	Do you hear?
[00:30.02]COMINIUS	Yet one time he did call me by my name:
[00:33.23]	I urged our old acquaintance, and the drops
[00:36.72]	That we have bled together. Coriolanus
[00:39.86]	He would not answer to: forbad all names;
[00:43.14]	He was a kind of nothing, titleless,
[00:46.06]	Till he had forged himself a name o' the fire
[00:49.70]	Of burning Rome.
[00:51.27]MENENIUS	Why, so: you have made good work!
[00:53.91]	A pair of tribunes that have rack'd for Rome,
[00:57.54]	To make coals cheap,--a noble memory!
[01:00.47]COMINIUS	I minded him how royal 'twas to pardon
[01:03.60]	When it was less expected: he replied,
[01:06.67]	It was a bare petition of a state
[01:09.52]	To one whom they had punish'd.
